Body:
He placed therein firm hills rising above it, and blessed it and
			measured therein its sustenance in four Days, alike for (all) who
			ask;

But if they turn away, then say: I warn you of a thunderbolt like
			the thunderbolt (which fell of old upon the tribes) of Aad and
			Thamud;

And though they are resigned, yet the Fire is still their home;
			and if they ask for favor, yet they are not of those unto whom
			favor can be shown.
